trans-unit.source: Represents a cell in a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel" />.
trans-unit.target: 表示 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel" /> 中的儲存格。

trans-unit.source: The following example shows how to use <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition> to set the position of a child control in a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanel> control.

trans-unit.source: Specifies whether this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" /> contains the same row and column as the specified <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" />.
trans-unit.target: 指定這個 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" /> 是否包含與指定 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" /> 相同的資料列和資料行。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="other" /> is a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" /> and has the same row and column as the specified <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <paramref name="other" /> 是 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" />，且具有與指定 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" /> 相同的資料列和資料行，則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The result specifies whether the values of the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition.Row" /> and <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition.Column" /> properties of the two <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TableLayoutPanelCellPosition" /> objects are unequal.
